Docker Desktop's built-in Kubernetes UI only shows the `default` namespace. Switch the namespace dropdown to see `medinovai-services`, `medinovai-ai`, `ingress-nginx`, etc. The full Kubernetes Dashboard at `https://localhost:8443` shows all namespaces.

