## Backup Rule (Always Enforce)

Run `scripts/backup.sh` before:
- Any `kubectl apply` that modifies the cluster
- Any compose file change
- Any `scripts/seed.sh --reset`
- Any Makefile infra target that changes state

Backups go to: `~/medinovai-backups/medinovai-Deploy/{db,volumes,config}/`

